# ims-client build-time environment (SRS §18.4 · FEV-03)
# VITE_ variables are baked into the bundle — PUBLIC BY DEFINITION (SEC §7).
# Never put a secret here. Validated at bootstrap by src/config (fail-fast).

VITE_API_BASE_URL=              # API origin for this environment, e.g. https://api.example.com
